    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head type="title"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #L1 #L2 #M">Index XXV.</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">Index XVI.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R">Index XXIIII.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Index XXIV. de Vladislai posthumi regis
                            auspiciis</rdg>
                    </app></head>
                <p>
                <s n="1">﻿In ea urbe, ubi de rebus agendis multa dicta <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #M">agitataque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">agitaque</rdg>
                    </app> sunt, decretum tandem, ut eo convenirent ex omni Hungaria optimates, a
                    quibus in novelli regis verba iuraretur.</s>
                <s n="2">Itaque ut primum omnes convenere, de more a singulis iuratum, fecit id ante <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">omnes</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">alios</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S2 #S3 #M">Ioannes</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S1">Ioannns</rdg>
                    </app> Corvinus, qui et sponte sua summo illo magistratu, quem octo annis magna
                    cum laude gesserat, se coram universo conventu abdicavit.</s>
                <s n="3">Rex autem prudentum quorundam consilio usus illi et <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Bistricensem</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B">Istrigensem</rdg>
                    </app> contulit comitatum et, quo se abdicavit, magistratum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">continuo</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M"/>
                    </app> restituit, post haec eum rex <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">egregie</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">aegregie</rdg>
                    </app> laudatum magnificeque donatum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">remisit in Hungariam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">in Hungariam remisit</rdg>
                    </app> una et omnem <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">illam Hungarorum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Hungarorum illam</rdg>
                    </app> nobilitatem, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">que</rdg>
                    </app> Viennam gratia rei, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">que</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">memorata</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">commemorata</rdg>
                    </app> est, convenerat.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">1–3 =Th
                    4.51.</note></s>
                <s n="4">Interiecto dein tempore perrexit rex ad suum regnum, ingressusque est Budam
                    anno ab ortu salvatoris mundi MCCCCLIII.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">4 = Th
                        4.53. – Et ab eo error oritur: rex Vienna Posonium indeque Pragam fecit
                        iter, ubi nuncium de expugnatione Constantinopolis accepit; primum quidem 6.
                        Februarii 1456. Budam advenit.</note></s>
                <s n="5"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Illic</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">Il-Illic</rdg>
                    </app> dum commoratur, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #L2">accipit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">accepit</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">Mahammectum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Mahammettum</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #M">Mahamettum</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2 #S3">Mahumetum</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#R">Mahametum</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2">Mahumetem</rdg>
                    </app> Turcarum imperatorem, qui nuper <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">Amoracto</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #R #M">Amoratto</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">Amorato</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">Amurato</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Amurate</rdg>
                    </app> patre defuncto in illius successerat et imperium et opes, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #M">expugnata</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S2 #S3">exgugnata</rdg>
                    </app> iam urbe Constantinopoli parare expeditionem in <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">Hungaria</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Hungariam</rdg>
                    </app>, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">percrebuisseque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">percraebuisseque</rdg>
                    </app> rumorem illum et iam adventare et velle <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">invadendae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">invadende</rdg>
                    </app> eius principium facere a <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #M">Taurino</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Tauruno</rdg>
                    </app>, quod oppidum magis vulgato vocabulo Belgradum cognominatur.</s>
                <s n="6">Nihil itaque ulterius ibi demoratus noctu una cum Ulrico Ciliae comite,
                    cuius consilio <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">praecipue</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">precipue</rdg>
                    </app> regebatur, inde abiit <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Viennamque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">Viennam</rdg>
                    </app> profectus est.</s>
                <s n="7">In ea quippe urbe ab Turcarum impetu arbitrati sunt Germani, qui regebant
                    regem, se tutiores fore, de regni vero salute nihil ab Ulrico et a <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S3 #M">ceteris</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2">caeteris</rdg>
                    </app>, qui regem adolescentem regebant, cogitatum, ideo res ipsa indicavit,
                    quod Budensem arcem sine ullo praesidio deseruere, putabant enim eum, qui tam
                    brevi temporis intervallo expugnasset Constantinopolim <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">Graecorumque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Graecorum</rdg>
                    </app> adeo facile <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">extinxisset</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">exstinxisset</rdg>
                    </app> imperium, prima irruptione primoque impetu ac una tantum excursione
                    universam sibi subacturum Hungariam cum ei <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">adiacentibus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">adiecentibus</rdg>
                    </app> regionibus.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">5–7 = Th 4.55. – 5 <hi
                            rend="italic">Illic... Constantinopoli</hi> = Th 4.54.</note></s>
                <s n="8">Satis superque de rege huc usque dixerim, de bello a <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">Mahammecto</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Mahammetto</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #M">Mahometto</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">Mahumeto</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#R">Mahometo</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Mahumete</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">suscepto</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B">suscaepto</rdg>
                    </app>, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #M">quemadmodum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">qnemadmodum</rdg>
                    </app> gestum finitumque sit, pauca subiicienda sunt.</s>
                <s n="9">Id equidem omittendum non <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">censui</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">caensui</rdg>
                    </app>, ne mihi <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">praetermitteretur</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">pretermitteretur</rdg>
                    </app> immortalitate digna laus, quam Ioannes Corvinus eo bello sibi comparavit,
                    suo <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">nanque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">namque</rdg>
                    </app> ductu atque auspiciis causa dei <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #M">defensa</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">desenfa</rdg>
                    </app> est, quippe qui sine <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">regis</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">regiis</rdg>
                    </app> auxiliis paucitate autem militum non solum obstitit potentissimi hostis
                    viribus, sed eo etiam rem usque deduxit, ut ille victus <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #M">coeptam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #L1 #L2">caeptam</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">ceptam</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">omiserit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #M">obmiserit</rdg>
                    </app> expeditionem, amissaque magna suarum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">copiarum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2"/>
                    </app> parte in rem malam eo, unde venerat, hoc est in Thraciam, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1">rediverit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z">redirit</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">redierit</rdg>
                    </app>.</s>
            </p>
